{"tid":2039100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［再世路亦十六］中國讚賞法國對香港問題採謹慎態度","createTime":"2020-05-28T00:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T02:05:40.000Z","uid":143343,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d26614b47a5c3282ea6018d16cbf38b6e998c028","tid":2039100,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:27:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392452\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392452&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=b8e3b6e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392452&h=0888e7f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=392452</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】國際關注港區國安法審議，外長王毅重申，此舉要填補香港在國家安全立法領域的漏洞，不會影響香港的高度自治，反而有利於推動一國兩制行穩致遠。<br />\n<br />\n國務委員兼外長王毅與法國總統外事顧問博納通電話，談及港區國安法審議。王毅表示，全國人大根據憲法和基本法，建立健全香港維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制，合理合法，有利推動一國兩制行穩致遠，各國投資者利益得到更好保障，中方並讚賞法國在涉港問題採取謹慎態度，希望能夠堅持客觀公正立場。<br />\n<br />\n法方就指尊重中國國家主權，無意介入香港事務，希望問題能夠在一國兩制框架下妥善解決。德國政府發言人認為，香港應該維持高度自治，期望北京尊重香港法治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望有生之年能夠見到法國收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1232c42be3041614d9561f89960db6d0b7e933","tid":2039100,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:29:30.000Z","msg":"馬卡龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b711a84accb244027d9ea86f176ae2c54f41bb6","tid":2039100,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:29:36.000Z","msg":"法蘭西淪落到幫支共奶鞋底"},{"pid":"96db23bb30997d04c269f64188427a199d23bc62","tid":2039100,"uid"